    <string name="changelog_text_v1_0_3">🔹 Direct access to book details by tapping its cover in Activity.
🔹 Option to follow users directly from reviews.
🔹 It is now possible to reply and like ActivityPub posts.
🔹 Reviews are sorted from newest to oldest.
🔹 Fixed the bug when publishing reviews and follower counters.
🔹 Internal stability improvements and reduced battery consumption.</string>
